So....wat I want to know is, what do I need to focus on in this Elo, an how to get out of it.
 {{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
I main: {{champion:268}} {{champion:119}} {{champion:64}} {{champion:412}} {{champion:75}} {{champion:56}} {{champion:19}}
Now...........Some say stick to smaller champ pools an that some of these champs r too hard or whatever. Bitch....I made it from Bronze 4 to Gold V playing {{champion:268}}  Lee Sin just doesn&#039;t work for this elo, so i normally pick {{champion:56}} or {{champion:19}} both amazing/broken champs you could ever play. I switch between crit an Lethal Noc, 1 shot wonder, an usually pick Warwick if a tank is needed. I pick {{champion:75}} If I really want to tryhard, usually destroying top lane an winning late, but completely understanding if the rest of us feed. {{champion:412}} Is my support pick if I get auto filled, do all I can to keep the team alive. Not much to say about him.. {{champion:119}} was my hard stuck bronze 1 champion, won games, lost games, couldnt escape from that hell because of my toxicity, So I started maining {{champion:75}}.
{{champion:64}} Is my favourite jungle/all around champion, doesn&#039;t get boring, I usually get really fed whilst playing him, mainly play norms with him, since lee Gold Elo is pointless......Thanks for reading this...&quot;help&quot;........&quot;me&quot; 
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
